item.title: About
item.description: About Me Yueming Yang Shandong University|SDU · School of Energy and Power Engineering Master Degree Candidate Research Interest Yueming Yang research interests are the design and optimization of supercritical CO2 turbomachinery (mainly radial inflow turbines and centrifugal compressors); modeling of fluid- and thermo- dynamic systems (mainly the SCO2 Brayton cycles); and physical properties of working fluid in circulation system (mainly the SCO2 power cycles). Education 2016.9 – 2020.6 Bachelor’s Degree in Engineering
